ADDITIONAL TERMS:

1. SELF-HOSTED USAGE LIMITS
Self-hosted instances of this software are subject to the following default limits:
- 50 messages per user per day
- $10 USD monthly budget per user

These limits may be modified via environment variables for personal use.
Commercial use exceeding these limits requires a commercial license.

2. COMMERCIAL LICENSE
Commercial use of this software at scale (exceeding self-hosted limits) or
without source disclosure obligations is available under a separate commercial license.

Contact: blah.chat@bhekani.com for commercial licensing inquiries.

3. NETWORK USE DISCLOSURE
As required by AGPLv3 Section 13, if you modify this software and make it
available over a network, you must provide users with access to the modified
source code.
